Callback funtion means  a function who waits for certain event trigger then that function will start performing 
 document.querySelectorAll(".drum")[i].addEventListener("click",handleClick(){

   
    
    var buttonInnerHTML= this.innerHTML;
    makeSound(buttonInnerHTML);
    
});

in this syntax handleClick() is call back funtion which get excuted when someone press particular drum/ anything on which event listner is putted
